parameters: In the Demo build, you can't leave the Stratum I Plateau!
\C[18]You're about to descend to the First Stratum.\.\. The content past this point is still being worked on.\C[0]
\c[18]Proceeding past this point will likely result in getting stuck and/or dying horribly.\c[0]
When Neneko first regains consciousness,\. it's to her body feeling sore all over.\.\. She squirms,\. groaning,\. slowly rolling over.\.\.
Her eyes open as she pushes herself up.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Mnng...\.\.\. Feel like I got flattened...\.\.\. who hit me?\.\. *cough*
She looks around,\. twitching her ears.\.\. There's a creak nearby,\. its source up higher,\. disappearing over the tall walls surrounding her.\.\.
The one side of the platform she found herself on that did not lead up,\. instead lead down.\.\. Was she...\.\.\. in some kind of cave...?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>That's right...\.\.\. I was fighting that afro bitch...\.\.\. then there was a boom and the lift fell...\.\.\.
Neneko stands up,\. wobbling on her feet.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Damnit...\.\.\. guh...\.\.\. okay,\. this must be...\.\.\. somewhere down below.\.\. Looks like I got blown onto a ledge instead of falling straight down to the bottom of the Lift...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Nyaha!\.\. That 'fro bitch couldn't stop me~!\.\. Must have been my feline instincts!
\n<\n[1]>Guess I'll have to climb down...\.\.\. maybe after my head stops spinning,\. nya...\.\.\.
spend time camp to reset Relationship
\n<\n[1]>The fallen lift...\.\.\. that sure was scary...
\n<\n[1]>But the afro bitch can't reach us now!\.\. Nyaha~
